elements.expression:
filters
| essql query="SELECT COUNT(*) AS Count FROM \"pmon_*\""
| markdown 
  "### SI3000
# Performance Monitoring System

Congratulations! You're using performance monitoring system to monitor performances.

Features:
- Support for legacy CDR and history files
- Call statistics
- KPI calculation
- Scalable
- Cluster setup
"
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT COUNT(*) AS Count FROM \"pmon_cdr_*\""
| math "Count"
| metric "Metrics collected" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=36 align="center" color="#000000" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"} metricFormat="0,0.[000]"
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT nodeName FROM \"pmon_inventory*\""
| math "unique(nodeName)"
| metric "Monitored objects" 
  metricFont={font size=48 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center" lHeight=48} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"} metricFormat="0,0.[000]"
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT COUNT(*) AS Calls, nodeName AS Node FROM \"pmon_cdr_node_calls*\" GROUP BY nodeName LIMIT 15"
| pointseries color="Node" size="Calls"
| pie
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT version FROM \"metricslib*\""
| markdown "MetricsLib version:
{{#each rows}}
 **{{version}}**
{{/each}}
"
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown 
  "### Reports tree structure

#### Node CDR

- [Node report](http://mcrk-docker-1:5601/app/dashboards#/view/2d1e51b0-f990-11ea-98d2-77c9ea127217).
- [Node tables](http://mcrk-docker-1:5601/app/dashboards#/view/e6b593f0-16ea-11eb-92e1-b5caf531bdb5)
 - [Average call duration](http://mcrk-docker-1:5601/app/dashboards#/view/31e1b510-f9af-11ea-98d2-77c9ea127217)

#### Trunk group reports
- asf
- asdfdsf

#### Subscriber group
- sd
- ljofd"
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT nodeName AS Node FROM \"pmon_inventory*\""
| markdown 
  "### SI3000 Performance Monitoring

Monitored nodes ({{rows.length}} rows):  
{{#each rows}}
{{Node}},
{{/each}}

"
| render
